<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li><p>99 students. Sample response: <m>24 + 13 =37</m> <m>37+40+77</m> <m>77+22=99</m></p></li>
      <li><p>35 students. Sample response: <m>13 + 22 = ?</m> <m>13 + 2 = 15</m> <m>15 + 20 = 35</m></p></li>
